---
---

<section id="soluzione" class="bg-brand-navy py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand-green">
        La soluzione
      </p>
      <h2
        class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        Una piattaforma. <span class="text-brand-green">Tre vittorie</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/70">
        ArenaBoostX collega tifosi, sponsor e club in un unico flusso di valore. Ognuno trova
        ciò che cerca, tutti crescono insieme.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 lg:mt-20 lg:gap-8">
      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-brand-green lg:p-10"
      >
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-brand-green">
          Per i tifosi
        </p>
        <svg
          class="mt-5 h-14 w-14 text-brand-green"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3.5" />
          <path d="M2.5 20c0-3.6 2.91-6 6.5-6s6.5 2.4 6.5 6" />
          <circle cx="17" cy="9" r="2.5" />
          <path d="M15 14.5c2.5 0 6.5 1.5 6.5 5" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Sempre vicini al club
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/70">
          Trasforma ogni tifoso in protagonista. Quiz live durante la partita, missioni
          settimanali, contenuti esclusivi: un motivo per restare connessi 365 giorni
          l'anno.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Esperienze interattive durante e fuori dagli eventi
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Gamification con punti, livelli e ricompense
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Contenuti esclusivi riservati ai veri tifosi
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-brand-green lg:p-10"
      >
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-brand-green">
          Per gli sponsor
        </p>
        <svg
          class="mt-5 h-14 w-14 text-brand-green"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5.5" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Investimenti che ripagano
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/70">
          Dai loghi statici alle attivazioni misurabili. Ogni sponsor partecipa attivamente
          all'esperienza, con dati precisi su engagement, reach e conversioni.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Attivazioni digitali integrate negli eventi
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Reportistica chiara con metriche di ROI
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Targeting per profili e comportamento
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-brand-green lg:p-10"
      >
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-brand-green">
          Per i club
        </p>
        <svg
          class="mt-5 h-14 w-14 text-brand-green"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path d="M3 4.5v13.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 4.5 19.5H21" />
          <path d="M6.5 15.5l4.5-4.5 3 3 5.5-5.5" />
          <path d="M14.5 8.5h5v5" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Ricavi che si moltiplicano
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/70">
          Nuovi flussi di ricavi oltre biglietti e abbonamenti. Una base tifosi profilata,
          fidelizzata e pronta a generare valore stagione dopo stagione.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Database tifosi profilato e proprietario
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Nuovi pacchetti commerciali per gli sponsor
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.25"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M4 10.5l3.5 3.5 8.5-9" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">
              Fidelizzazione che riduce il churn stagionale
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-6 text-center lg:mt-20">
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/80">
        Tutti gli stakeholder. Una sola piattaforma. Risultati misurabili.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#contatti"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-green px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-[#00d9a4] hover:shadow-md focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-green focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-brand-navy"
      >
        Richiedi una demo
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
